title: Only You ( Kim Tae Woo )
lyrics: Eoneusae nae anen neoui sumsori man Eoneusae nae anen neoui moksori man Ireo ke neo hana man Geuriun i bam eotteo khae I bami jinamye on geudaero dallyeo ga Doraboji anko geudaero dallyeo ga Ireo ke neo hana man Bogo sipeun bam eotteo khae Oh don't you remember Daedaphaej wo geu maeum sok naega isseo? Yes I can remember Neol gidar yeo nae maeum sok neo hana man Nan neo hana man eoneusae nae anen.. Oh Oh Don't you remember Eoneusae nae anen.. Oh Oh Haengbokhal tende.. cham haengbokhal tende..
